messages.agent_message: Have you been in contact or close to someone with COVID-19?
Are you experiencing symptoms of any kind? (Answer yes or no).
Has it been at least 5 days since you were exposed to COVID-19?
Have you contracted COVID-19 in the last 30 days?
How about in the last 90 days?
Although you don't have symptoms, since it has been 5 days, you should test. You can use either a PCR test or take antigen tests according to the suggested testing guidelines.
